      <title>开发环境配置</title>
      <link href="/p/6b3d/"/>
      <url>/p/6b3d/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Before"><a href="#Before" class="headerlink" title="Before"></a>Before</h2><p>记录一些开发工具，sdk，数据库配置信息。省的到处百度google。</p><span id="more"></span><ul><li>javascript</li><li>mysql</li></ul><h2 id="JavaScript"><a href="#JavaScript" class="headerlink" title="JavaScript"></a>JavaScript</h2><h3 id="Node"><a href="#Node" class="headerlink" title="Node"></a>Node</h3><p>在用户目录下新建 <strong>.npmrc</strong> 文件：</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">registry</span>=https://registry.npm.taobao.org/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">cache</span>=D:\Cache\npm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>缓存路径自己自定义</p></li><li><p><strong>强烈不推荐 使用npm，他只是个 yarn下载器</strong></p></li></ul><h3 id="nvm-windows"><a href="#nvm-windows" class="headerlink" title="nvm-windows"></a>nvm-windows</h3><p>安装这个程序实现多node版本切换</p><ul><li><p>配置node的实体位置：<code>nvm root [path]</code></p></li><li><p>配置node的下载镜像站：<code>nvm node_mirror https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/node/</code></p></li><li><p>配置npm的下载镜像站：<code>nvm npm_mirror https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/npm/</code> (虽然 .npmrc 设置过了)</p></li></ul><p><strong>切换命令一定要使用管理员权限执行</strong></p><h3 id="nvm"><a href="#nvm" class="headerlink" title="nvm"></a>nvm</h3><p>Unix 系统下的多node版本切换</p><h3 id="Yarn"><a href="#Yarn" class="headerlink" title="Yarn"></a>Yarn</h3><ul><li><p>在用户目录下新建 .yarnrc 文件</p></li><li><p><code>npm i -g yarn</code></p></li><li><p><code>yarn config set 变量名 变量值</code></p><p>可配置属性</p><table><thead><tr><th>变量名</th><th>变量值</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>regitstry</td><td>“<a href="https://registry.npm.taobao.org”/">https://registry.npm.taobao.org”</a></td><td>仓库镜像源</td></tr><tr><td>cache-folder</td><td>“D:\\Cache\\yarn”</td><td>依赖缓存</td></tr><tr><td>global-folder</td><td>“D:\\Sdk\\yarn”</td><td>全局模块</td></tr><tr><td>prefix</td><td>“D:\\Sdk\\yarn”</td><td>模块可执行二进制文件</td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>小彩蛋，在 .yarnrc 添加一行  <code>“--emoji</code> true</em> 执行yarn命令会有可爱的表情哦。</p></li><li><p>yarn 自举</p><p><code>yarn global add yarn</code></p><p><code>npm rm -g yarn</code></p></li></ul><h2 id="MySQL"><a href="#MySQL" class="headerlink" title="MySQL"></a>MySQL</h2><p>官网下载 win-zip版 解压到指定目录，添加文件 <code>my.ini</code>:</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[mysqld]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">port</span> = <span class="number">3306</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">basedir</span>=<span class="string">&quot;D:\\Sdk\\mysql-8.0.26&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">datadir</span>=<span class="string">&quot;E:\\Store\\mysql\\data&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tmpdir</span>=<span class="string">&quot;D:\\Cache\\mysql&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">character-set-server</span>=utf8mb4</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">max_connections</span>=<span class="number">20</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">max_connect_errors</span>=<span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">default-storage-engine</span>=INNODB</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[client]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">port</span>=<span class="number">3306</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[mysql]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">default-character-set</span>=utf8mb4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>初始化data，管理员 <code>mysqld --console --initialize</code></li><li>注册服务，管理员<code>mysqld --install</code></li><li>删除服务，管理员<code>mysqld --remove</code></li><li>首次登陆，一定要重新设置root密码。</li><li>推荐使用 第三方的python版 mysql 命令行客户端：mycli <code>pip install mycli</code></li></ul><h2 id="MongoDB"><a href="#MongoDB" class="headerlink" title="MongoDB"></a>MongoDB</h2><p>下载zip版 解压到指定目录，</p><p>新建文件 mongodb.conf</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">noauth</span> = <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">dbpath</span> = E:\db\data</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">logpath</span> = E:\db\mongodb.log<span class="comment"># 这个一定是个文件绝对路径</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">logappend</span> = <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">bind_ip</span> = <span class="number">127.0</span>.<span class="number">0.1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">port</span> = <span class="number">27017</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">journal</span> = <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">quiet</span> = <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>命令行启用数据库，必带配置参数 <code>mongod --config ./mongodb.conf</code></p><p>windows 可以写到 ps 的$PROFILE里，方便调用。</p><h2 id="Python"><a href="#Python" class="headerlink" title="Python"></a>Python</h2><h3 id="pip-ini"><a href="#pip-ini" class="headerlink" title="pip.ini"></a>pip.ini</h3><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[global]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">index-url</span> = https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple/</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">[install]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">trusted-host</span> = pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>unix 系统下 .config/pip.cnf</p><h2 id="Vim"><a href="#Vim" class="headerlink" title="Vim"></a>Vim</h2><h3 id="vimrc"><a href="#vimrc" class="headerlink" title=".vimrc"></a>.vimrc</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">set nobackup</span><br><span class="line">set noundofile</span><br><span class="line">set nu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="PowerShell"><a href="#PowerShell" class="headerlink" title="PowerShell"></a>PowerShell</h2><p>$PROFILE</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Import-Module</span> posh<span class="literal">-git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-PoshPrompt</span> robbyrussel</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cls</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">su</span></span>&#123; <span class="built_in">start-process</span> wt <span class="literal">-verb</span> runas &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">setpxy</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable">$env:http_proxy</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://127.0.0.1:23333&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable">$env:https_proxy</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://127.0.0.1:23333&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">unsetpxy</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">del</span> env:http_proxy</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">del</span> env:https_proxy</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>( (<span class="built_in">pwd</span>).Path <span class="operator">-eq</span> <span class="string">&quot;C:\Windows\System32&quot;</span> ) &#123;<span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="variable">$HOME</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-Alias</span> <span class="literal">-Name</span> py <span class="literal">-Value</span> python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装两个模块</p><p><code> Install-Module posh-git oh-my-posh</code></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
